attributes.value: Fearless: Displays fearlessness in the face of danger bravely defending itself or its territory.
Whispered Secrets: Possesses the ability to hear and share whispered secrets gaining valuable information.
Sleepwalker: Occasionally engaging in sleepwalking episodes stumbling around while asleep.

metadata.name: Power Cat #001: Salem
metadata.description: Salem: Born in the mystical realm of Witches' Hollow, Salem is a mischievous Power Cat with a lineage tied to ancient sorcery. Legend has it that a witch's familiar bestowed magical powers upon him, granting him the ability to manipulate shadows and cast enchantments.
